The paper focuses on building nearest neighbor search solutions on top of full-text search engines, which is a topic closely related to information retrieval (cs.IR). Additionally, the paper specifically addresses the task of NNS in Hamming space, which is a common problem in computer vision (cs.CV) and data mining (cs.DS, cs.DB). The paper also proposes a novel engineering solution, which could be of interest to the machine learning community (cs.LG).
